// - Vertex input: vec2<f32> position in data coords
// - Uniforms: clip-space transform + baseline value + solid RGBA color
// - Topology: triangle-strip
// - CPU duplicates vertices as p0,p0,p1,p1,... and we use vertex_index parity:
